INSTALL

You should run these three lines:

cd downloader
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh

USING

6 programs will be installed

1. dlmaker

Makes download.sh at current directory

2. dllist

Lists downloads

3. downloader

Starts download. You should run "downloader -y" command in one tab and "downloader -n" in another one. (or you can use them as different jobs)

4. killdler

Stops downloader (and the second one will start)
If you want to kill all downloaders, you can use "-f" argument

5. dl

Starts download without any advanced things

6. killer

This command is not about downloader. It kills every process which has the given name. The "killer" command is used by other commands such as "downloader" or "dl"